{"tid":2359024,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 秦式焗羊架","createTime":"2021-01-08T14:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T07:45:43.000Z","uid":260581,"like":33,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"093f342e67323f257db7fe348a1015a453b9c2c3","tid":2359024,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NDT13C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NDT13C.jpg&h=8d5cd4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAmROJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAmROJD.jpg&h=6e69a053&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcE76vj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcE76vj.jpg&h=cc1d3555&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBH2aW0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBH2aW0.jpg&h=8acd968e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日行超市見到特價，100hkd 12支骨<br />\n<br />\n因為我聽日想係屋企bbq,所以今日食一半，聽日食一半就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nD羊架既最佳日期係聽日前食用，但我打開都臭臭地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用左秦式既萬能醃法，芫荽、蒜蓉、辣椒、魚露、<br />\n糖、檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後200度，每邊5分鐘，然後230-250度，燒爐模式，燒佢幾分鐘，食落冇臭，最好食係下面d芫荽蒜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4243239ca789731ecbb445eb142e4f8e6e1bafa","tid":2359024,"uid":17123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"fat"},{"pid":"5e7b7efd5b316cd161eb959bdad23098a0b6fdff","tid":2359024,"uid":209310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:21:53.000Z","msg":"fat"},{"pid":"cc095407611e5cd5d1df3646b0c66251673d5244","tid":2359024,"uid":2